\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Conclusion and further work}
\begin{itemize}
\item We have point out some restrictions when Piper diagrams is used to analyse water geochemistry,
\item We have adjusted a finite mixture to explain the water geochemistry of our sample,
\item We have proposed an methodology to extract a hierarchy from a fixed parametric model,
\item Some methodology need to be applied to overcome spacial dependecies.
\end{itemize}
